data.description: Lovely full brick one level home located in the Golden Springs community. This 4 bedroom 2 bath home offers gleaming hardwood floors throughout, formal living and dining rooms, kitchen is complete with stainless steel double ovens, electric cook-top and eating area overlooking the bay window. Family room has brick wood burning fireplace, both baths with dual vanities and a fabulous sun room.
data.whatILove: Full Brick rancher with Partial basement which would be a great workshop space.  Four (4) Bedrooms and 2 Full Baths (Both have soaking tubs).  Kitchen has eat in area with new appliances.  New and spacious Sunroom located on back of house (12' by 22').  Fireplace in Den and large 2 car Garage.
